[[File:SEO Economic Research logo.jpg|thumb|360px|SEO Economic Research logo]] '''SEO Economic Research''' ('''SEO''') is a [[Research institute|scientific institute]] for economic research commissioned by [[Ministry (government department)|ministries]] or businesses.<ref>Stichting voor Economisch Onderzoek der Universiteit van Amsterdam (9159) ''Tien jaar speurwerk door de Stichting voor Economisch Onderzoek der Universiteit van Amsterdam 1949-1959''. Leiden.</ref>
SEO was founded in '''1949''' from the Faculty of Economics of the [[University of Amsterdam]]. It is an independent institute, affiliated with the university. Until 2005 it was called "Stichting voor Economisch Onderzoek der Universiteit van Amsterdam" (Foundation for Economic Research of the University of Amsterdam).
